Hello Valeria,
&nbsp;
Good Day!
&nbsp;
Upon checking about your requirement, i would like to provide the details of my observation and how the box packing method works in our app.
&nbsp;
For the order 1413, the app is considering two boxes to pack the products. The Generic (Config 1) box is considered to pack all 6 quantities of SPL102 and 8 quantities of RCH205-I. The remaining 8 quantities of RCH205-I are getting packed in Generic (Config 2) box.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
This is because, the app uses an algorithm to pack the products optimally and looks to reduce the wastage of the space.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Also, the following criteria is considered by the app during the packing of the products and selection of a suitable box.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
  The length, width, and height of the product are compared individually to the length, width, and height of the box.  Total Volume of all the items in the order must be less than the box's volume.  Total Weight of all items in the order should be less than the MaxWeight limit of the box.  If the "Stack" option is enabled, the height of all products is summed up to determine the best-fitting box.  &nbsp;
Boundary conditions like rotating the product are not considered in the box packing method.
To get a better understanding of how the box packing strategy works with our app, please refer to this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cdt2hqF6wRU
&nbsp;
For the current order, the app see that only two boxes can be used for the packaging instead of 3 boxes considering all the above mentioned criteria.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Also, the app is considering the Generic (Config 1) box and the Generic (Config 2) box for packaging due to the following.
&nbsp;
  The app see that 6 quantities of SPL102 and 8 quantities of RCH205-I can be packed in Config 1 box as this box can hold upto 24.9 kg and the total weight of 6 quantities of SPL102 and 8 quantities of RCH205-I is 24.86 kg.&nbsp;
&nbsp;  The app then considered the Config 2 box as this box size and volume is lesser than that of the box 8 x RS2+/RS3 and also can hold remaining 8 quantities.&nbsp;  &nbsp;
Please note that it is not possible to pack a certain product into a certain box automatically at all times as the package settings is global and works based on all the above criteria mentioned and also considering less wastage of space.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
So, for your specific requirements, we recommend to consider package editing for the orders.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Sagar K S
Team PluginHive

